name: Codacy Badger
bio: Review less, merge faster. Check code style, security, duplication, complexity and coverage on every change while tracking code quality throughout your sprints.

name: fossabot
bio: Your friendly neighborhood FOSSA bot. Opens PRs to add a @fossas scan status to your README. Also opens PRs to remediate vulnerabilities in your dependencies.

name: Snyk bot
bio: Snyk's bot, opens pull requests to fix known vulnerabilities in your dependencies. Check out https://snyk.io/ to learn more.
